item.title: Aircraft Model Collection in 2014
item.description: Some nonsenses… This post covers all my aircraft models which collected in 2014. Time flies very fasts…There was a large number models back to 2014. However, only 4 girls remained here today. ID Photo and Basic Information: Official China Southwest Airlines B757-200, B-2820. This is not a typical “model” but she stayed in my home over 20 years. Arrived before A.D.2000. Dragonwings Airbus A310-300 Prototype, no registration number.
